<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="29May1917"><font color="red">29 May 1917</font>, <cite>NYPL</cite> (JJ to John Quinn): [Mentions receiving a letter the previous day from an agent in New York named L. Bloom at 274 W. 19th Street] Do you know him? I confess I am rather superstitious about it for it is the name of the chief character in the book I am writing <cite>Ulysses</cite>. </div>
